{
  "0": "[Slide 1] Technology Stack & IP Protection\nWe’re building on Ethereum using Solidity for smart contracts, which gives us access to a robust, battle‑tested ecosystem. Our backend runs on Node.js with Express, fully hosted on AWS (EC2 for compute, RDS for relational data, S3 for static assets). Security is reinforced by OpenZeppelin libraries, ensuring best‑in‑class contract hygiene.\nOn the IP side, we have two patents pending – one covering a novel consensus‑layer optimization that reduces finality latency, and another for a cross‑chain bridge design that improves liquidity flow. Our tokenomics model is a trade secret, giving us a competitive moat without disclosing sensitive parameters to the market."
}
